  "subject": "[Bug] HTTP 431 Request Header Fields Too Large",
  "commit_message": "[Bug] HTTP 431 Request Header Fields Too Large\n\n- The incoming request seems to be containing the header size to me more\n  than the default of 8KB. So exposing the env variable to override the\n  parameter as per the agreed requirement.\n- HTTP_MAX_REQUEST_HEADER_SIZE needs to be set to override the size.\n  Defaults to 8KB\n\nIssue-ID: CPS-2297\nChange-Id: Icada84a54e645b1a6edcb576d53bfd476ef9a6c5\nSigned-off-by: mpriyank <priyank.maheshwari@est.tech>\n",
